theorem
(for V being  Abelian non empty RLSStruct holds (for M being (Subset of V) holds (M is  convex implies (for r being Real holds ((( 0 ) < r & r < 1) implies ( ( ( 1 - r ) * M ) + ( r * M ) ) c= M)))))
proof
