((ex w1 being (Element of V) st (u = ( ( 1 - r ) * w1 ) & w1 in M)) & (ex w2 being (Element of V) st (v = ( r * w2 ) & w2 in M))) by A4;
hence thesis by A1,A2,A3,CKB2:def 1;
end;
